{"tid":85732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死2隻]湖北兄弟爛醉跌倒　被當獵物開槍雙亡","createTime":"2017-01-18T14:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T15:30:07.000Z","uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7641e285f889432ed698faf698f53ba5a65c831","tid":85732,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:11:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170118/1038156\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170118%2F1038156&d=97fExk77nkGkdEDbKyWwYXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=8b9564ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170118/1038156</a><br />\n<br />\n中國湖北近日發生打獵物誤擊事件，2男跌入草叢被當獵物擊斃。<br />\n新華社記者今天從警局獲悉，上周四晚間9時30分，大同鎮葛山村村民周姓三兄弟途徑獅子鎮東山村路段時，一人飲酒後站立不穩滑入山溝，其他兩人為拉他一同滑進溝內草叢。<br />\n三人向上爬過程中，守候在附近的獵人左男、汪男等人，見草叢中有激烈動靜，誤以為是獵物。左男持單管獵槍向搖晃草叢開槍，結果擊中2人死亡。<br />\n目前獵人左男、汪男被依法刑事拘留。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ee30fc3dc30594f6918f722aff5d9cc97d8132","tid":85732,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"冇認錯，禽獸"}]}